Preheat to oven to 200C/180C Fan/Gas 6.Tip the beans, peas, tomatoes, oregano, chilli flakes and tomato pur√©e into a roasting tin and toss together. Bake for 15 minutes. For the last few minutes of cooking, put the tacos on a baking tray and warm in the oven.Meanwhile, mash together the avocado, lemon juice and coriander.Carefully tip the beans into a serving bowl. Put the tacos, beans, avocado, cheese and soured cream in separate bowls on the table so everyone can help themselves.